Name: Wolfie's Break Out
About the game: Back in my day we had to go outside and to a place called 'The Arcade' to play video games. take a trip back to simplistic controls and try to beat your high-score or even challenge your friend to beat it with this retro arcade brick breaking game Why all you need is a mouse to move the paddle back and forth whilst keeping the ball in play A throw back to the old school brick breaker games! Keep your brain fit with this game
